                  <a href="/frequently-asked-questions">
                    <img alt="" title="Frequently Asked Questions" src="/resources/images/about-jb/faq.png" width="98" border="0">
                  </a>
                </figure>
                <p>
                  Many of the questions that you might have are already answered in our FAQ section. If you don't find what you need, you can submit your question to us!
                  <a class="jb-feature-brand-moreinfo" href="/frequently-asked-questions">View More ►</a>
                </p>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </li>
        
        
        <li class="jb-feature-brand-listing">
            <div class="jb-feature-brand-item">
