                  <a href="/fundraising-and-vending">
                    <img alt="" title="Vending &amp; Fundraising Programs" src="/resources/images/about-jb/vending.png" width="98" border="0">
                  </a>
                </figure>
                <p>
                   Learn more about our vending &amp; fundraising program. Jelly Belly candy makes for an extremely profitable alternative.
                  <a class="jb-feature-brand-moreinfo" href="/fundraising-and-vending">View More ►</a>
                </p>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </li>
        
        
        <li class="jb-feature-brand-listing">
            <div class="jb-feature-brand-item">
