                    <img alt="" title="Educators &amp; Students" src="/resources/images/about-jb/students.jpg" width="133" border="0">
                  </a>
                </figure>
                <p>
                 Are you a student or educator looking for information regarding the Jelly Belly Candy Company? Get the scoop on useful information about the company on our Educators &amp; Students page.
